                        <interp inst="t18520510-name-258" type="surname" value="MANN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18520510-name-258" type="given" value="CALEB SCHOLEFIELD"></interp>CALEB SCHOLEFIELD MANN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a clerk, in the Steam Navigation Com<lb></lb>pany. I was in the Skin market, Leadenhall, on 7th May; I felt something touch my pocket—I turned round and saw the prisoner close to me, raising his hand from my pocket, with my handkerchief in his hand—he put it to his face, I seized him directly, and gave him into custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> There was a man between him and me; I was two or three yards from him. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> No; he was close to me.</p>
